brogan.description:
A friendly hero in range gains 1 coin;
if any hero was defeated this round,
that friendly hero gains 3 coins instead.

A friendly hero in range gains 2 coin2;
if any hero was defeated this round,
that friendly hero gains 4 coins instead.

emmitt.description:
You may play two cards each turn;
if you do, after the cards are revealed,
retrieve one of your unresolved cards.

min.description:
Swap with a ::token_smoke_bomb:: Smoke bomb in range;
if you do, block the attack. You may place
the Smoke bomb into a space in range.

razzle.description:
Push an unit adjacent to you up to 2 spaces;
for every space the target moved, move this
one of you one space in the opposite direction.

Push an unit adjacent to you up to 3 spaces;
for every space the target moved, move this
one of you one space in the opposite direction.

sabina.description:
If there are two or more friendly minions in
radius, you may retrieve a discarded card;
if you do, you may move 1 space.

If there are two or more friendly minions in
radius, you may retrieve a discarded card;
if you do, you may up to 2 spaces.

snorri.description:
Target a unit adjacent to you;
if a rune is active:

::rune_bird::: You may target a minion in range instead.
::rune_axe::: +3 ::attack_gold:: Attack
::rune_anvil::: If you target a hero, gain 3 coins.
::rune_horn::: Repeat once on a different hero in range.

Target a hero adjacent to you;
if a rune is active:

::rune_axe::: +3 ::attack_gold:: Attack
::rune_anvil::: Gain 2 coins.
::rune_horn::: Repeat once on a different hero in range.

If a rune is active:
::rune_horn::: Block a basic attack;
::rune_axe::: Block a non-ranged attack;
::rune_bird::: Block a ranged attack;
**This Turn:** You are immune to enemy actions.

Choose one active rune:
::rune_horn::: Block a basic attack;
::rune_axe::: Block a non-ranged attack;
::rune_bird::: Block a ranged attack;
::rune_anvil::: Block a non-basic attack;
**This Turn:** You are immune to enemy actions.

tigerclaw.description:
Move up to 2 spaces.  Take 1 or 2 coins
from an enemy hero adjacent to you;
if you do, you may move up to 2 spaces.

xargatha.description:
Before or after movement, you may move
an enemy minion in radius up to 2 spaces;
ignore heavy minion immunity.
